If youre using Java 8 you can use its features to sort your list, [this][2] article shows good examples of that, it takes a bit more work but seems like what you&#39;re after. Note that in order to convert from `stream` to `list` you have to include  `.collect(Collectors.toList());` at the end of the `stream`. 

Example(taken from the article): 

